{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u34461355\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">取消重复请求是前端性能优化中比较重要的一环，尤其是在搜索、提交表单、实时过滤等场景。重复请求不仅浪费网络资源和服务器开销，还可能导致数据覆盖或 UI 闪动。下面分场景介绍几种常见的解决方案。</span></p><hr id=\"hzK4W\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"SmzZC\"><span class=\"ne-text\">一、防抖与节流（限制请求发起频率）</span></h3><p id=\"ub1b4137b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这是最直接的方法，通过控制请求的触发时机来避免重复请求。</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ude982b54\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">防抖</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在指定时间内只执行最后一次操作。常用于输入框搜索。</span></li><li id=\"u06552e03\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">节流</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在指定时间内只执行第一次操作。常用于按钮点击、滚动加载。</span></li></ul><h4 id=\"z34mH\"><span class=\"ne-text\">示例：输入框搜索防抖</span></h4><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"j68tM\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>let timer;\nfunction search(keyword) {\n  clearTimeout(timer);\n  timer = setTimeout(() =&gt; {\n    fetch(`/api/search?q=${keyword}`).then(/* ... */);\n  }, 300);\n}</code></pre><hr id=\"dJfl7\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"yCLnF\"><span class=\"ne-text\">二、基于 AbortController 取消请求</span></h3><p id=\"u36112ccb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">现代浏览器提供了 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">AbortController</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 接口，可以用来取消一个或多个 Fetch 请求。Axios 也支持该方式（v0.22.0+）。</span></p><h4 id=\"zRNvl\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 使用 Fetch + AbortController</span></h4><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"bknhi\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>let controller = null;\n\nfunction search(keyword) {\n  // 如果之前有请求，先取消\n  if (controller) {\n    controller.abort();\n  }\n  controller = new AbortController();\n\n  fetch(`/api/search?q=${keyword}`, { signal: controller.signal })\n    .then(response =&gt; response.json())\n    .then(data =&gt; console.log(data))\n    .catch(err =&gt; {\n      if (err.name === 'AbortError') {\n        console.log('请求已取消');\n      } else {\n        console.error('请求失败', err);\n      }\n    });\n}</code></pre><h4 id=\"rnTJq\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 使用 Axios + AbortController</span></h4><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"a4vUP\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>let cancelTokenSource;\n\nfunction search(keyword) {\n  if (cancelTokenSource) {\n    cancelTokenSource.cancel('取消重复请求');\n  }\n  cancelTokenSource = axios.CancelToken.source();\n\n  axios.get(`/api/search?q=${keyword}`, {\n    cancelToken: cancelTokenSource.token\n  }).then(response =&gt; {\n    console.log(response.data);\n  }).catch(thrown =&gt; {\n    if (axios.isCancel(thrown)) {\n      console.log('请求已取消', thrown.message);\n    } else {\n      // 处理其他错误\n    }\n  });\n}</code></pre><p id=\"u0101ada5\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">Axios 0.22.0 之后推荐使用 </span></strong><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">AbortController</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"SlrGh\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>let controller;\n\nfunction search(keyword) {\n  if (controller) controller.abort();\n  controller = new AbortController();\n\n  axios.get(`/api/search?q=${keyword}`, {\n    signal: controller.signal\n  }).then(response =&gt; {\n    console.log(response.data);\n  }).catch(error =&gt; {\n    if (error.name === 'AbortError' || error.code === 'ERR_CANCELED') {\n      console.log('请求已取消');\n    }\n  });\n}</code></pre><hr id=\"Z6WxN\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"tdKLp\"><span class=\"ne-text\">三、在组件卸载时取消未完成的请求</span></h3><p id=\"u531a3ca8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在单页应用中，如果组件已销毁但请求还未返回，可能会触发 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">setState</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 导致内存泄漏或报错。建议在组件卸载时取消所有挂起的请求。</span></p><h4 id=\"mMpet\"><span class=\"ne-text\">React 示例（使用 AbortController）</span></h4><pre data-language=\"jsx\" id=\"dhjmb\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-jsx\"><code>useEffect(() =&gt; {\n  const controller = new AbortController();\n\n  fetchData(controller.signal);\n\n  return () =&gt; {\n    controller.abort(); // 组件卸载时取消请求\n  };\n}, []);</code></pre><hr id=\"EFHPc\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"TMK9n\"><span class=\"ne-text\">四、全局管理请求（请求去重）</span></h3><p id=\"u1125c67e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">对于全局通用的请求（如获取用户信息、配置项），可以使用请求库（如 axios）的拦截器配合 Map 来管理 pending 请求，当新请求发起时取消之前相同的请求。</span></p><h4 id=\"W9QIs\"><span class=\"ne-text\">示例：基于请求 URL + 参数生成唯一 key</span></h4><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"I1Pxa\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>const pendingMap = new Map();\n\nfunction generateReqKey(config) {\n  return [config.method, config.url, JSON.stringify(config.params), JSON.stringify(config.data)].join('&amp;');\n}\n\nfunction addPendingRequest(config) {\n  const key = generateReqKey(config);\n  if (pendingMap.has(key)) {\n    const controller = pendingMap.get(key);\n    controller.abort(); // 取消之前的请求\n    pendingMap.delete(key);\n  }\n  const controller = new AbortController();\n  config.signal = controller.signal;\n  pendingMap.set(key, controller);\n}\n\n// 请求拦截器\naxios.interceptors.request.use(config =&gt; {\n  addPendingRequest(config);\n  return config;\n});\n\n// 响应拦截器\naxios.interceptors.response.use(response =&gt; {\n  const key = generateReqKey(response.config);\n  pendingMap.delete(key);\n  return response;\n}, error =&gt; {\n  if (error.name !== 'AbortError') {\n    const key = generateReqKey(error.config);\n    pendingMap.delete(key);\n  }\n  return Promise.reject(error);\n});</code></pre><hr id=\"i4CDI\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"DpIwe\"><span class=\"ne-text\">五、业务层面的防重复提交</span></h3><p id=\"u248ceb81\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">对于表单提交、支付等操作，可以使用</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮 loading 状态</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">或</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">全局遮罩</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">防止用户二次点击。</span></p><pre data-language=\"jsx\" id=\"lkXyR\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-jsx\"><code>function handleSubmit() {\n  if (isSubmitting) return;\n  setIsSubmitting(true);\n  submitAPI().finally(() =&gt; setIsSubmitting(false));\n}</code></pre><hr id=\"wuV4m\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"bbs4v\"><span class=\"ne-text\">六、利用缓存避免重复请求</span></h3><p id=\"ued66f5a4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果数据在一定时间内不会变化，可以缓存首次请求的结果，后续直接使用缓存数据，不再发起请求。例如使用 SWR、React Query 等库，它们内部也有去重和缓存机制。</span></p><hr id=\"sJOgd\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"jqzYr\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ue7c54256\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">搜索类</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：防抖 + 取消前一次请求。</span></li><li id=\"ua8fdeeaf\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮点击类</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：节流或 loading 状态。</span></li><li id=\"u10069c91\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">全局重复请求</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：统一管理 pending 请求并取消。</span></li><li id=\"uce705ebd\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">组件卸载</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：利用生命周期取消请求，避免内存泄漏。</span></li></ul><p id=\"ufc8e94c6\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">根据业务场景选择合适的组合策略，能有效提升用户体验和系统性能。</span></p></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u34461355\" id=\"u34461355\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0aa6eca1\" id=\"u0aa6eca1\">取消重复请求是前端性能优化中比较重要的一环，尤其是在搜索、提交表单、实时过滤等场景。重复请求不仅浪费网络资源和服务器开销，还可能导致数据覆盖或 UI 闪动。下面分场景介绍几种常见的解决方案。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22hzK4W%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"SmzZC\" id=\"SmzZC\"><span data-lake-id=\"u52a5a427\" id=\"u52a5a427\">一、防抖与节流（限制请求发起频率）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ub1b4137b\" id=\"ub1b4137b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u319b5338\" id=\"u319b5338\">这是最直接的方法，通过控制请求的触发时机来避免重复请求。</span></p><ul list=\"ub9cf4549\"><li fid=\"u4f38a6f9\" data-lake-id=\"ude982b54\" id=\"ude982b54\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u19c8687a\" id=\"u19c8687a\">防抖</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6428f3b9\" id=\"u6428f3b9\">：在指定时间内只执行最后一次操作。常用于输入框搜索。</span></li><li fid=\"u4f38a6f9\" data-lake-id=\"u06552e03\" id=\"u06552e03\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1d550fdb\" id=\"u1d550fdb\">节流</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u936cc844\" id=\"u936cc844\">：在指定时间内只执行第一次操作。常用于按钮点击、滚动加载。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id=\"z34mH\" id=\"z34mH\"><span data-lake-id=\"u591c207e\" id=\"u591c207e\">示例：输入框搜索防抖</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22let%20timer%3B%5Cnfunction%20search(keyword)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20clearTimeout(timer)%3B%5Cn%20%20timer%20%3D%20setTimeout(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20fetch(%60%2Fapi%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%24%7Bkeyword%7D%60).then(%2F*%20...%20*%2F)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%2C%20300)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22j68tM%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22dJfl7%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"yCLnF\" id=\"yCLnF\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua505d4e0\" id=\"ua505d4e0\">二、基于 AbortController 取消请求</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u36112ccb\" id=\"u36112ccb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u17e214d3\" id=\"u17e214d3\">现代浏览器提供了 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf30132f5\" id=\"uf30132f5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58590c86\" id=\"u58590c86\">AbortController</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uae0fedf6\" id=\"uae0fedf6\"> 接口，可以用来取消一个或多个 Fetch 请求。Axios 也支持该方式（v0.22.0+）。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"zRNvl\" id=\"zRNvl\"><span data-lake-id=\"u17fc9287\" id=\"u17fc9287\">1. 使用 Fetch + AbortController</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22let%20controller%20%3D%20null%3B%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20search(keyword)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%88%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%5Cn%20%20if%20(controller)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20controller.abort()%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20controller%20%3D%20new%20AbortController()%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20fetch(%60%2Fapi%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%24%7Bkeyword%7D%60%2C%20%7B%20signal%3A%20controller.signal%20%7D)%5Cn%20%20%20%20.then(response%20%3D%3E%20response.json())%5Cn%20%20%20%20.then(data%20%3D%3E%20console.log(data))%5Cn%20%20%20%20.catch(err%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20if%20(err.name%20%3D%3D%3D%20'AbortError')%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20console.log('%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88')%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%20else%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20console.error('%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5'%2C%20err)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22bknhi%22%7D\"></card><h4 data-lake-id=\"rnTJq\" id=\"rnTJq\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud944c746\" id=\"ud944c746\">2. 使用 Axios + AbortController</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22let%20cancelTokenSource%3B%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20search(keyword)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(cancelTokenSource)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20cancelTokenSource.cancel('%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82')%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20cancelTokenSource%20%3D%20axios.CancelToken.source()%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20axios.get(%60%2Fapi%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%24%7Bkeyword%7D%60%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20cancelToken%3A%20cancelTokenSource.token%5Cn%20%20%7D).then(response%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20console.log(response.data)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D).catch(thrown%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20(axios.isCancel(thrown))%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20console.log('%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88'%2C%20thrown.message)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%20else%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22a4vUP%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u0101ada5\" id=\"u0101ada5\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0c0c1fb2\" id=\"u0c0c1fb2\">Axios 0.22.0 之后推荐使用 </span></strong><code data-lake-id=\"u1b084728\" id=\"u1b084728\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc946171\" id=\"ufc946171\">AbortController</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2fa91816\" id=\"u2fa91816\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22let%20controller%3B%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20search(keyword)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(controller)%20controller.abort()%3B%5Cn%20%20controller%20%3D%20new%20AbortController()%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20axios.get(%60%2Fapi%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%24%7Bkeyword%7D%60%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20signal%3A%20controller.signal%5Cn%20%20%7D).then(response%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20console.log(response.data)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D).catch(error%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20(error.name%20%3D%3D%3D%20'AbortError'%20%7C%7C%20error.code%20%3D%3D%3D%20'ERR_CANCELED')%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20console.log('%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88')%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22SlrGh%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22Z6WxN%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"tdKLp\" id=\"tdKLp\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua108b531\" id=\"ua108b531\">三、在组件卸载时取消未完成的请求</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u531a3ca8\" id=\"u531a3ca8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8b7e0bf5\" id=\"u8b7e0bf5\">在单页应用中，如果组件已销毁但请求还未返回，可能会触发 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud981e584\" id=\"ud981e584\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1afc66b3\" id=\"u1afc66b3\">setState</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6d3c9184\" id=\"u6d3c9184\"> 导致内存泄漏或报错。建议在组件卸载时取消所有挂起的请求。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"mMpet\" id=\"mMpet\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7fdcfc39\" id=\"u7fdcfc39\">React 示例（使用 AbortController）</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22jsx%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22useEffect(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20const%20controller%20%3D%20new%20AbortController()%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20fetchData(controller.signal)%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20return%20()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20controller.abort()%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%8D%B8%E8%BD%BD%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%5Cn%20%20%7D%3B%5Cn%7D%2C%20%5B%5D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22dhjmb%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22EFHPc%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"TMK9n\" id=\"TMK9n\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubf5caeae\" id=\"ubf5caeae\">四、全局管理请求（请求去重）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u1125c67e\" id=\"u1125c67e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub03d0287\" id=\"ub03d0287\">对于全局通用的请求（如获取用户信息、配置项），可以使用请求库（如 axios）的拦截器配合 Map 来管理 pending 请求，当新请求发起时取消之前相同的请求。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"W9QIs\" id=\"W9QIs\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufb4c31bf\" id=\"ufb4c31bf\">示例：基于请求 URL + 参数生成唯一 key</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20pendingMap%20%3D%20new%20Map()%3B%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20generateReqKey(config)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20return%20%5Bconfig.method%2C%20config.url%2C%20JSON.stringify(config.params)%2C%20JSON.stringify(config.data)%5D.join('%26')%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20addPendingRequest(config)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20const%20key%20%3D%20generateReqKey(config)%3B%5Cn%20%20if%20(pendingMap.has(key))%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20const%20controller%20%3D%20pendingMap.get(key)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20controller.abort()%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%5Cn%20%20%20%20pendingMap.delete(key)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20const%20controller%20%3D%20new%20AbortController()%3B%5Cn%20%20config.signal%20%3D%20controller.signal%3B%5Cn%20%20pendingMap.set(key%2C%20controller)%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8%5Cnaxios.interceptors.request.use(config%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20addPendingRequest(config)%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20config%3B%5Cn%7D)%3B%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8%5Cnaxios.interceptors.response.use(response%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20const%20key%20%3D%20generateReqKey(response.config)%3B%5Cn%20%20pendingMap.delete(key)%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20response%3B%5Cn%7D%2C%20error%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(error.name%20!%3D%3D%20'AbortError')%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20const%20key%20%3D%20generateReqKey(error.config)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20pendingMap.delete(key)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20return%20Promise.reject(error)%3B%5Cn%7D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22I1Pxa%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22i4CDI%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"DpIwe\" id=\"DpIwe\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4eaef668\" id=\"u4eaef668\">五、业务层面的防重复提交</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u248ceb81\" id=\"u248ceb81\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaed6b564\" id=\"uaed6b564\">对于表单提交、支付等操作，可以使用</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u12ff0852\" id=\"u12ff0852\">按钮 loading 状态</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u58ca23b7\" id=\"u58ca23b7\">或</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1430762b\" id=\"u1430762b\">全局遮罩</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u23a22658\" id=\"u23a22658\">防止用户二次点击。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22jsx%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22function%20handleSubmit()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(isSubmitting)%20return%3B%5Cn%20%20setIsSubmitting(true)%3B%5Cn%20%20submitAPI().finally(()%20%3D%3E%20setIsSubmitting(false))%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22lkXyR%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22wuV4m%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"bbs4v\" id=\"bbs4v\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc4e79af1\" id=\"uc4e79af1\">六、利用缓存避免重复请求</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ued66f5a4\" id=\"ued66f5a4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6b342a06\" id=\"u6b342a06\">如果数据在一定时间内不会变化，可以缓存首次请求的结果，后续直接使用缓存数据，不再发起请求。例如使用 SWR、React Query 等库，它们内部也有去重和缓存机制。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22sJOgd%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"jqzYr\" id=\"jqzYr\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubef8e455\" id=\"ubef8e455\">总结</span></h3><ul list=\"ueea34803\"><li fid=\"u729b8f10\" data-lake-id=\"ue7c54256\" id=\"ue7c54256\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8bec0151\" id=\"u8bec0151\">搜索类</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7feb6aa7\" id=\"u7feb6aa7\">：防抖 + 取消前一次请求。</span></li><li fid=\"u729b8f10\" data-lake-id=\"ua8fdeeaf\" id=\"ua8fdeeaf\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5bb2c7d6\" id=\"u5bb2c7d6\">按钮点击类</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u205e8c94\" id=\"u205e8c94\">：节流或 loading 状态。</span></li><li fid=\"u729b8f10\" data-lake-id=\"u10069c91\" id=\"u10069c91\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue90a5626\" id=\"ue90a5626\">全局重复请求</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u140b5d5a\" id=\"u140b5d5a\">：统一管理 pending 请求并取消。</span></li><li fid=\"u729b8f10\" data-lake-id=\"uce705ebd\" id=\"uce705ebd\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9ce5984d\" id=\"u9ce5984d\">组件卸载</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5f831f9d\" id=\"u5f831f9d\">：利用生命周期取消请求，避免内存泄漏。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ufc8e94c6\" id=\"ufc8e94c6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4c48beb1\" id=\"u4c48beb1\">根据业务场景选择合适的组合策略，能有效提升用户体验和系统性能。</span></p>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u34461355\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">取消重复请求是前端性能优化中比较重要的一环，尤其是在搜索、提交表单、实时过滤等场景。重复请求不仅浪费网络资源和服务器开销，还可能导致数据覆盖或 UI 闪动。下面分场景介绍几种常见的解决方案。</span></p><hr id=\"hzK4W\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"SmzZC\"><span class=\"ne-text\">一、防抖与节流（限制请求发起频率）</span></h3><p id=\"ub1b4137b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这是最直接的方法，通过控制请求的触发时机来避免重复请求。</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ude982b54\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">防抖</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在指定时间内只执行最后一次操作。常用于输入框搜索。</span></li><li id=\"u06552e03\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">节流</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在指定时间内只执行第一次操作。常用于按钮点击、滚动加载。</span></li></ul><h4 id=\"z34mH\"><span class=\"ne-text\">示例：输入框搜索防抖</span></h4><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"j68tM\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>let timer;\nfunction search(keyword) {\n  clearTimeout(timer);\n  timer = setTimeout(() =&gt; {\n    fetch(`/api/search?q=${keyword}`).then(/* ... */);\n  }, 300);\n}</code></pre><hr id=\"dJfl7\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"yCLnF\"><span class=\"ne-text\">二、基于 AbortController 取消请求</span></h3><p id=\"u36112ccb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">现代浏览器提供了 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">AbortController</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 接口，可以用来取消一个或多个 Fetch 请求。Axios 也支持该方式（v0.22.0+）。</span></p><h4 id=\"zRNvl\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 使用 Fetch + AbortController</span></h4><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"bknhi\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>let controller = null;\n\nfunction search(keyword) {\n  // 如果之前有请求，先取消\n  if (controller) {\n    controller.abort();\n  }\n  controller = new AbortController();\n\n  fetch(`/api/search?q=${keyword}`, { signal: controller.signal })\n    .then(response =&gt; response.json())\n    .then(data =&gt; console.log(data))\n    .catch(err =&gt; {\n      if (err.name === 'AbortError') {\n        console.log('请求已取消');\n      } else {\n        console.error('请求失败', err);\n      }\n    });\n}</code></pre><h4 id=\"rnTJq\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 使用 Axios + AbortController</span></h4><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"a4vUP\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>let cancelTokenSource;\n\nfunction search(keyword) {\n  if (cancelTokenSource) {\n    cancelTokenSource.cancel('取消重复请求');\n  }\n  cancelTokenSource = axios.CancelToken.source();\n\n  axios.get(`/api/search?q=${keyword}`, {\n    cancelToken: cancelTokenSource.token\n  }).then(response =&gt; {\n    console.log(response.data);\n  }).catch(thrown =&gt; {\n    if (axios.isCancel(thrown)) {\n      console.log('请求已取消', thrown.message);\n    } else {\n      // 处理其他错误\n    }\n  });\n}</code></pre><p id=\"u0101ada5\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">Axios 0.22.0 之后推荐使用 </span></strong><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">AbortController</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"SlrGh\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>let controller;\n\nfunction search(keyword) {\n  if (controller) controller.abort();\n  controller = new AbortController();\n\n  axios.get(`/api/search?q=${keyword}`, {\n    signal: controller.signal\n  }).then(response =&gt; {\n    console.log(response.data);\n  }).catch(error =&gt; {\n    if (error.name === 'AbortError' || error.code === 'ERR_CANCELED') {\n      console.log('请求已取消');\n    }\n  });\n}</code></pre><hr id=\"Z6WxN\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"tdKLp\"><span class=\"ne-text\">三、在组件卸载时取消未完成的请求</span></h3><p id=\"u531a3ca8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在单页应用中，如果组件已销毁但请求还未返回，可能会触发 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">setState</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 导致内存泄漏或报错。建议在组件卸载时取消所有挂起的请求。</span></p><h4 id=\"mMpet\"><span class=\"ne-text\">React 示例（使用 AbortController）</span></h4><pre data-language=\"jsx\" id=\"dhjmb\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-jsx\"><code>useEffect(() =&gt; {\n  const controller = new AbortController();\n\n  fetchData(controller.signal);\n\n  return () =&gt; {\n    controller.abort(); // 组件卸载时取消请求\n  };\n}, []);</code></pre><hr id=\"EFHPc\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"TMK9n\"><span class=\"ne-text\">四、全局管理请求（请求去重）</span></h3><p id=\"u1125c67e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">对于全局通用的请求（如获取用户信息、配置项），可以使用请求库（如 axios）的拦截器配合 Map 来管理 pending 请求，当新请求发起时取消之前相同的请求。</span></p><h4 id=\"W9QIs\"><span class=\"ne-text\">示例：基于请求 URL + 参数生成唯一 key</span></h4><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"I1Pxa\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>const pendingMap = new Map();\n\nfunction generateReqKey(config) {\n  return [config.method, config.url, JSON.stringify(config.params), JSON.stringify(config.data)].join('&amp;');\n}\n\nfunction addPendingRequest(config) {\n  const key = generateReqKey(config);\n  if (pendingMap.has(key)) {\n    const controller = pendingMap.get(key);\n    controller.abort(); // 取消之前的请求\n    pendingMap.delete(key);\n  }\n  const controller = new AbortController();\n  config.signal = controller.signal;\n  pendingMap.set(key, controller);\n}\n\n// 请求拦截器\naxios.interceptors.request.use(config =&gt; {\n  addPendingRequest(config);\n  return config;\n});\n\n// 响应拦截器\naxios.interceptors.response.use(response =&gt; {\n  const key = generateReqKey(response.config);\n  pendingMap.delete(key);\n  return response;\n}, error =&gt; {\n  if (error.name !== 'AbortError') {\n    const key = generateReqKey(error.config);\n    pendingMap.delete(key);\n  }\n  return Promise.reject(error);\n});</code></pre><hr id=\"i4CDI\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"DpIwe\"><span class=\"ne-text\">五、业务层面的防重复提交</span></h3><p id=\"u248ceb81\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">对于表单提交、支付等操作，可以使用</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮 loading 状态</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">或</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">全局遮罩</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">防止用户二次点击。</span></p><pre data-language=\"jsx\" id=\"lkXyR\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-jsx\"><code>function handleSubmit() {\n  if (isSubmitting) return;\n  setIsSubmitting(true);\n  submitAPI().finally(() =&gt; setIsSubmitting(false));\n}</code></pre><hr id=\"wuV4m\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"bbs4v\"><span class=\"ne-text\">六、利用缓存避免重复请求</span></h3><p id=\"ued66f5a4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果数据在一定时间内不会变化，可以缓存首次请求的结果，后续直接使用缓存数据，不再发起请求。例如使用 SWR、React Query 等库，它们内部也有去重和缓存机制。</span></p><hr id=\"sJOgd\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"jqzYr\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ue7c54256\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">搜索类</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：防抖 + 取消前一次请求。</span></li><li id=\"ua8fdeeaf\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮点击类</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：节流或 loading 状态。</span></li><li id=\"u10069c91\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">全局重复请求</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：统一管理 pending 请求并取消。</span></li><li id=\"uce705ebd\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">组件卸载</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：利用生命周期取消请求，避免内存泄漏。</span></li></ul><p id=\"ufc8e94c6\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">根据业务场景选择合适的组合策略，能有效提升用户体验和系统性能。</span></p></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u34461355\" id=\"u34461355\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0aa6eca1\" id=\"u0aa6eca1\">取消重复请求是前端性能优化中比较重要的一环，尤其是在搜索、提交表单、实时过滤等场景。重复请求不仅浪费网络资源和服务器开销，还可能导致数据覆盖或 UI 闪动。下面分场景介绍几种常见的解决方案。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22hzK4W%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"SmzZC\" id=\"SmzZC\"><span data-lake-id=\"u52a5a427\" id=\"u52a5a427\">一、防抖与节流（限制请求发起频率）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ub1b4137b\" id=\"ub1b4137b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u319b5338\" id=\"u319b5338\">这是最直接的方法，通过控制请求的触发时机来避免重复请求。</span></p><ul list=\"ub9cf4549\"><li fid=\"u4f38a6f9\" data-lake-id=\"ude982b54\" id=\"ude982b54\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u19c8687a\" id=\"u19c8687a\">防抖</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6428f3b9\" id=\"u6428f3b9\">：在指定时间内只执行最后一次操作。常用于输入框搜索。</span></li><li fid=\"u4f38a6f9\" data-lake-id=\"u06552e03\" id=\"u06552e03\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1d550fdb\" id=\"u1d550fdb\">节流</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u936cc844\" id=\"u936cc844\">：在指定时间内只执行第一次操作。常用于按钮点击、滚动加载。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id=\"z34mH\" id=\"z34mH\"><span data-lake-id=\"u591c207e\" id=\"u591c207e\">示例：输入框搜索防抖</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22let%20timer%3B%5Cnfunction%20search(keyword)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20clearTimeout(timer)%3B%5Cn%20%20timer%20%3D%20setTimeout(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20fetch(%60%2Fapi%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%24%7Bkeyword%7D%60).then(%2F*%20...%20*%2F)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%2C%20300)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22j68tM%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22dJfl7%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"yCLnF\" id=\"yCLnF\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua505d4e0\" id=\"ua505d4e0\">二、基于 AbortController 取消请求</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u36112ccb\" id=\"u36112ccb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u17e214d3\" id=\"u17e214d3\">现代浏览器提供了 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf30132f5\" id=\"uf30132f5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58590c86\" id=\"u58590c86\">AbortController</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uae0fedf6\" id=\"uae0fedf6\"> 接口，可以用来取消一个或多个 Fetch 请求。Axios 也支持该方式（v0.22.0+）。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"zRNvl\" id=\"zRNvl\"><span data-lake-id=\"u17fc9287\" id=\"u17fc9287\">1. 使用 Fetch + AbortController</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22let%20controller%20%3D%20null%3B%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20search(keyword)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%88%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%5Cn%20%20if%20(controller)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20controller.abort()%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20controller%20%3D%20new%20AbortController()%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20fetch(%60%2Fapi%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%24%7Bkeyword%7D%60%2C%20%7B%20signal%3A%20controller.signal%20%7D)%5Cn%20%20%20%20.then(response%20%3D%3E%20response.json())%5Cn%20%20%20%20.then(data%20%3D%3E%20console.log(data))%5Cn%20%20%20%20.catch(err%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20if%20(err.name%20%3D%3D%3D%20'AbortError')%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20console.log('%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88')%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%20else%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20console.error('%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5'%2C%20err)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22bknhi%22%7D\"></card><h4 data-lake-id=\"rnTJq\" id=\"rnTJq\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud944c746\" id=\"ud944c746\">2. 使用 Axios + AbortController</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22let%20cancelTokenSource%3B%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20search(keyword)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(cancelTokenSource)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20cancelTokenSource.cancel('%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82')%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20cancelTokenSource%20%3D%20axios.CancelToken.source()%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20axios.get(%60%2Fapi%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%24%7Bkeyword%7D%60%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20cancelToken%3A%20cancelTokenSource.token%5Cn%20%20%7D).then(response%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20console.log(response.data)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D).catch(thrown%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20(axios.isCancel(thrown))%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20console.log('%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88'%2C%20thrown.message)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%20else%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22a4vUP%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u0101ada5\" id=\"u0101ada5\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0c0c1fb2\" id=\"u0c0c1fb2\">Axios 0.22.0 之后推荐使用 </span></strong><code data-lake-id=\"u1b084728\" id=\"u1b084728\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc946171\" id=\"ufc946171\">AbortController</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2fa91816\" id=\"u2fa91816\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22let%20controller%3B%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20search(keyword)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(controller)%20controller.abort()%3B%5Cn%20%20controller%20%3D%20new%20AbortController()%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20axios.get(%60%2Fapi%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%24%7Bkeyword%7D%60%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20signal%3A%20controller.signal%5Cn%20%20%7D).then(response%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20console.log(response.data)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D).catch(error%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20(error.name%20%3D%3D%3D%20'AbortError'%20%7C%7C%20error.code%20%3D%3D%3D%20'ERR_CANCELED')%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20console.log('%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88')%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%7D)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22SlrGh%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22Z6WxN%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"tdKLp\" id=\"tdKLp\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua108b531\" id=\"ua108b531\">三、在组件卸载时取消未完成的请求</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u531a3ca8\" id=\"u531a3ca8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8b7e0bf5\" id=\"u8b7e0bf5\">在单页应用中，如果组件已销毁但请求还未返回，可能会触发 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud981e584\" id=\"ud981e584\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1afc66b3\" id=\"u1afc66b3\">setState</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6d3c9184\" id=\"u6d3c9184\"> 导致内存泄漏或报错。建议在组件卸载时取消所有挂起的请求。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"mMpet\" id=\"mMpet\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7fdcfc39\" id=\"u7fdcfc39\">React 示例（使用 AbortController）</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22jsx%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22useEffect(()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20const%20controller%20%3D%20new%20AbortController()%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20fetchData(controller.signal)%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20return%20()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20controller.abort()%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%8D%B8%E8%BD%BD%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%5Cn%20%20%7D%3B%5Cn%7D%2C%20%5B%5D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22dhjmb%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22EFHPc%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"TMK9n\" id=\"TMK9n\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubf5caeae\" id=\"ubf5caeae\">四、全局管理请求（请求去重）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u1125c67e\" id=\"u1125c67e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub03d0287\" id=\"ub03d0287\">对于全局通用的请求（如获取用户信息、配置项），可以使用请求库（如 axios）的拦截器配合 Map 来管理 pending 请求，当新请求发起时取消之前相同的请求。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"W9QIs\" id=\"W9QIs\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufb4c31bf\" id=\"ufb4c31bf\">示例：基于请求 URL + 参数生成唯一 key</span></h4><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20pendingMap%20%3D%20new%20Map()%3B%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20generateReqKey(config)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20return%20%5Bconfig.method%2C%20config.url%2C%20JSON.stringify(config.params)%2C%20JSON.stringify(config.data)%5D.join('%26')%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20addPendingRequest(config)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20const%20key%20%3D%20generateReqKey(config)%3B%5Cn%20%20if%20(pendingMap.has(key))%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20const%20controller%20%3D%20pendingMap.get(key)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20controller.abort()%3B%20%2F%2F%20%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%5Cn%20%20%20%20pendingMap.delete(key)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20const%20controller%20%3D%20new%20AbortController()%3B%5Cn%20%20config.signal%20%3D%20controller.signal%3B%5Cn%20%20pendingMap.set(key%2C%20controller)%3B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8%5Cnaxios.interceptors.request.use(config%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20addPendingRequest(config)%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20config%3B%5Cn%7D)%3B%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8%5Cnaxios.interceptors.response.use(response%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20const%20key%20%3D%20generateReqKey(response.config)%3B%5Cn%20%20pendingMap.delete(key)%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20response%3B%5Cn%7D%2C%20error%20%3D%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(error.name%20!%3D%3D%20'AbortError')%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20const%20key%20%3D%20generateReqKey(error.config)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20pendingMap.delete(key)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20return%20Promise.reject(error)%3B%5Cn%7D)%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22I1Pxa%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22i4CDI%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"DpIwe\" id=\"DpIwe\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4eaef668\" id=\"u4eaef668\">五、业务层面的防重复提交</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u248ceb81\" id=\"u248ceb81\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaed6b564\" id=\"uaed6b564\">对于表单提交、支付等操作，可以使用</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u12ff0852\" id=\"u12ff0852\">按钮 loading 状态</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u58ca23b7\" id=\"u58ca23b7\">或</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1430762b\" id=\"u1430762b\">全局遮罩</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u23a22658\" id=\"u23a22658\">防止用户二次点击。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22jsx%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22function%20handleSubmit()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20if%20(isSubmitting)%20return%3B%5Cn%20%20setIsSubmitting(true)%3B%5Cn%20%20submitAPI().finally(()%20%3D%3E%20setIsSubmitting(false))%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22lkXyR%22%7D\"></card><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22wuV4m%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"bbs4v\" id=\"bbs4v\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc4e79af1\" id=\"uc4e79af1\">六、利用缓存避免重复请求</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ued66f5a4\" id=\"ued66f5a4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6b342a06\" id=\"u6b342a06\">如果数据在一定时间内不会变化，可以缓存首次请求的结果，后续直接使用缓存数据，不再发起请求。例如使用 SWR、React Query 等库，它们内部也有去重和缓存机制。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22sJOgd%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"jqzYr\" id=\"jqzYr\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubef8e455\" id=\"ubef8e455\">总结</span></h3><ul list=\"ueea34803\"><li fid=\"u729b8f10\" data-lake-id=\"ue7c54256\" id=\"ue7c54256\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8bec0151\" id=\"u8bec0151\">搜索类</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7feb6aa7\" id=\"u7feb6aa7\">：防抖 + 取消前一次请求。</span></li><li fid=\"u729b8f10\" data-lake-id=\"ua8fdeeaf\" id=\"ua8fdeeaf\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5bb2c7d6\" id=\"u5bb2c7d6\">按钮点击类</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u205e8c94\" id=\"u205e8c94\">：节流或 loading 状态。</span></li><li fid=\"u729b8f10\" data-lake-id=\"u10069c91\" id=\"u10069c91\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue90a5626\" id=\"ue90a5626\">全局重复请求</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u140b5d5a\" id=\"u140b5d5a\">：统一管理 pending 请求并取消。</span></li><li fid=\"u729b8f10\" data-lake-id=\"uce705ebd\" id=\"uce705ebd\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9ce5984d\" id=\"u9ce5984d\">组件卸载</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5f831f9d\" id=\"u5f831f9d\">：利用生命周期取消请求，避免内存泄漏。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ufc8e94c6\" id=\"ufc8e94c6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4c48beb1\" id=\"u4c48beb1\">根据业务场景选择合适的组合策略，能有效提升用户体验和系统性能。</span></p>","word_count":998,"slug":"dnmn98416ovxyq3i","type":"Doc","title":"如何取消重复请求？","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"取消重复请求是前端性能优化中比较重要的一环，尤其是在搜索、提交表单、实时过滤等场景。重复请求不仅浪费网络资源和服务器开销，还可能导致数据覆盖或 UI 闪动。下面分场景介绍几种常见的解决方案。一、防抖与节流（限制请求发起频率）这是最直接的方法，通过控制请求的触发时机来避免重复请求。防抖：在指定时...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"hr\":7,\"codeblock\":7}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-02-26T08:44:28.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-02-26T08:47:30.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-02-26T08:47:29.882Z","content_updated_at":"2026-02-26T08:47:30.000Z","id":258014472},"doc_digest":"1hzrI4z4Nqlqs9ntmer2CXSNgMY"}